dict.string: SortedOrder required if you have patched SSDTs in ACPI/patched
The following fixes may be needed for onboard audio/USB/etc
change OSID to XSID (to avoid match against _OSI XOSI patch)
change _OSI to XOSI, pair with SSDT-XOSI.aml
change EC0 to EC, optionally pair with SSDT-BAT0.aml
change HDAS to HDEF, optionally pair with SSDT-HDEF.aml
change Method(GPRW,2,N) to XPRW, pair with SSDT-PRW.aml
change GFX0 to IGPU, optionally pair with SSDT-IGPU.aml
change Method(_Q10,0,N) to XQ10, optionally pair with SSDT-FN.aml
change Method(_Q11,0,N) to XQ11, optionally pair with SSDT-FN.aml
change SAT0 to SATA, optionally pair with SSDT-SATA.aml
To avoid automatic Clover fake device-id (Skylake) injection
Disable panic kext logging on 10.13 Debug kernel
Disable panic kext logging on 10.13 Release kernel
MSR 0xE2 _xcpm_idle instant reboot(c) Pike R. Alpha
change F%uT%04x to F%uTxxxx in AppleBacklightInjector.kext (credit RehabMan)
Increase 15 port limit to 26 in AppleUSBXHCIPCI
Change 15 Port Limit To 30 in XHCI Kext 10.12(99-series)
